(define/contract (maximum-triplet-value nums)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)
  (let ([n (length nums)])
    (let loop ([i 0] [max-value 0])
      (if (= i (- n 2))
          max-value
          (let loop-j ([j (+ i 1)] [current-max max-value])
            (if (= j (- n 1))
                (loop (+ i 1) current-max)
                (let loop-k ([k (+ j 1)] [inner-max current-max])
                  (if (= k n)
                      (loop-j (+ j 1) inner-max)
                      (let ([value (* (- (list-ref nums i) (list-ref nums j)) (list-ref nums k))])
                        (loop-k (+ k 1) (max inner-max (if (< value 0) 0 value))))))))))))
